      <title>五角大楼同意与 LGBTQ+ 退伍军人就退伍身份达成历史性诉讼和解</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/01/06/nx-s1-5250269/pentagon-lawsuit-lgbtq-veterans-benefits</link>
